IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.T_STBooking') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_STBooking
GO

    [tms_booking_allocateddate] datetime2(7),
    [tms_booking_assetreleasedate] datetime2(7),

    [tms_booking_cargoweight] float,
    [tms_booking_customerid] bigint,
    [tms_booking_childcustomerid] bigint,
    [tms_booking_insby] bigint,
    [tms_booking_insbyname] nvarchar(4000),
    [tms_booking_cref1] nvarchar(4000),
    [tms_booking_cref2] nvarchar(4000),
    [tms_booking_cubicvolume] float,
    [tms_booking_customeragreedrate] bigint,
    [tms_booking_customerrate] bigint,
    [tms_booking_deliverydate] datetime2(7),
    [tms_booking_directbooking] int,
    [tms_booking_dispatchdate] datetime2(7),
    [tms_booking_docdate] datetime2(7),
    [tms_booking_docstatus] nvarchar(4000),
    [tms_booking_emailrequester] nvarchar(4000),

    [tms_booking_note] nvarchar(4000),

    [tms_booking_tobranchid] bigint,
    [tms_booking_trailersize] nvarchar(4000),
    [tms_booking_trailertype] nvarchar(4000),
    [tms_booking_transporter] nvarchar(4000),
    [tms_booking_tripid] bigint,
    [tms_booking_reason] nvarchar(4000),
    [tms_booking_source] nvarchar(4000),
    [tms_booking_type] nvarchar(4000),

	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/OPS/stbooking.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO
